      Data: 32|UnityEngine.HeaderAttribute, UnityEngine.CoreModule
    - Name: header
      Entry: 1
      Data: '

        Check Debug Mode boolean if you are actively experimenting
        with swimming values in inspector


        This allows swimming values to
        update repeatedly instead of only once per scene load.


        Otherwise,
        leave boolean as unchecked.'
